            <description><![CDATA[<h2>RepoBar 0.6.3</h2>
<ul>
<li>Make the Settings Repository table columns sortable (thanks @XueshiQiao).</li>
<li>Improve copied GitHub reference parsing for maintainer triage lists so bullet-leading references stay prioritized, compound issue lists resolve, and status counts are ignored.</li>
</ul>
<p><a href="https://github.com/steipete/RepoBar/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md">View full changelog</a></p>
]]></description>
